adjust the shape_width and shape_height to match the bbox size of the tracing object.

points_to_sample means the time it will take (points = frames) to travel through the spline from the start point to the end. It can differ from the project frame count to achieve more controllable results.

Spline Editor now supports multiple splnes. Right Click and select Add New Spline to add new trajectory.

It's recommended to separate character motion trajectories and camera motion trajectories into different Spline Editors.

It's recommended to avoid trajectory shape intersection between trajectories and separate them into two different motion videos.
Combining multiple motion video to one if no shape intersection.
